ing: 1 (8 ounce) package cream cheese with chives
1 (10.75 ounce) can  condensed cream of shrimp soup
des: "Warm shrimp dip. To be served with potato chips or crackers. Serve soon after making because it cools quickly!!"
ins: In a large skillet, combine cream cheese, and cream cheese with chives. When the cheese has melted, mix in shrimp soup, Worcestershire sauce, and shrimp. Stir until the mixture is heated through.
